original_title: 特命戦隊ゴーバスターズ ファイナルライブツアー2013
overview: A live show that was performed across Japan in March and April of 2013, acting as a final farewell for the cast. It comprises two parts: a scripted show part, and a talk show with the cast. The Kyoryugers also appear.
tagline: Finally, the Final Battle! Busters, Ready... Go!!
title: Tokumei Sentai Go-Busters Final Live Tour 2013
